<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Wikiful</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>

  <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>

 <nav class="navbar navbar-default" role="navigation">
 	<div class="container-fluid">
 		<div class="navbar-header">
 			<%= link_to "Wikiful", root_path, :class => "navbar-brand" %>
   		</div>
		<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
        	<li>Eventually log in/out and sign up links will go here</li>
        </ul>
   	</div>
</nav>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-9"><%= yield %></div> 
      <div class="col-md-3 sidebar">
        <div class="my-wiki-site">
      <h4>My Wikiful</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "Write a Wiki", new_article_path %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="categories-sidebar">
      <h4>Categories</h4>
      <ul>
        <% @categories.each do |category| %>
          <li><%= link_to category.title, category %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="about">
      <h4>About Wikiful</h4>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusantium architecto earum neque perspiciatis quia animi debitis quod repellat vitae explicabo. Sapiente aliquam reprehenderit id vitae atque ducimus facere molestias soluta?</p>
    </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
